text: Jørgen Jensen (2 June 1939 - 12 March 1995) was a Danish wrestler. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:1995 deaths Category:Danish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Denmark Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Copenhagen
